search_results.title: Episode 32: Greg Hinze
search_results.snippet: Meet Greg Hinze: Three time North American Bridge Champion, world champion and he also has a world class sense of humor!

search_results.title: Gregory Hinze at Yakima Valley College
search_results.snippet: Greg Hinze was my favorite professor. He's not with us anymore, but the lessons I learned from him are the ones I use repeatedly.

search_results.title: comments by Greg Hinze
search_results.snippet: My question though is if they made a movie about you, who would you like to play the role? April 10, 2014. In the Well: Sabine Auken · Greg Hinze.
